data.title: Bursheba Leighton Fristoe Younger (1816
data.meta_description: Bursheba Leighton Fristoe Younger was the daughter of Judge Richard Marshall Fristoe and Mary Leighton Sullivan. Born on the 6th day of June 1816 she was married to Henry Washington Younger in 1830 and became the mother of 14 children with only 13 living into adulthood. She loved the smell of spring lilac outside her...
